{"title":"How small is the M4 Mac mini really? This small","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2514485/how-small-is-the-m4-mac-mini-really-this-small.html","date":1731061800000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>The new <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/2512911/m4-pro-mac-mini-review-remarkably-small-and-incredibly-powerful.html\">M4 Mac mini</a> is… mini. It’s way more mini than the old mini, which wasn’t a very big desktop computer at all. At just 5×5 inches square and 2 inches tall, it’s less than a quarter the volume of the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/1948425/mac-studio-m2-max-review.html\">Mac Studio</a>, which is also a small desktop computer, and only 1.33 inches bigger than the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/1373000/apple-tv-4k-3rd-generation-review.html\">Apple TV 4K</a> in length and width and not even an inch taller.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But what does that really <em>mean?</em> How does that size compare to other everyday objects? Perhaps these photos will provide a better point of reference for just how mini Apple’s new Mac mini really is.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini vs Magic Trackpad\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5127w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-trackpad.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s something you may have already: A Magic Trackpad. Its footprint actually exceeds that of the new Mac mini. It’s thinner, of course, but just know that a Magic Trackpad takes up more room on your desk than a Mac mini.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini iPhone 16 Pro Max\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 6000w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-iphone.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Even placed diagonally, the iPhone 16 Pro Max extends well beyond the boundaries of the new Mac mini.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini playing cards\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5523w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-cards.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Is it bigger than a couple of decks of standard playing cards? Yes, of course, it’s not <em>that</em> tiny. But it’s not as much bigger as you’d expect.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini coffee\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5905w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-coffee.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you love coffee? Me, too. But I bet you’re not used to your coffee mug <em>dwarfing your desktop computer</em>.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini PS5\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5958w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-ps5.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Even a PS5 DualSense controller is bulkier than the Mac mini.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini smoke detector\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5920w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-smoke-detector.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s a great way to visualize the Mac mini: stack two standard household smoke detectors on top of each other. That’s almost exactly how big this little computer is.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"M4 Mac mini sunglasses\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 5991w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=1200%2C800&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=1240%2C826&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/m4-mac-mini-glasses.jpg?resize=150%2C100&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>I don’t know about you, but I certainly don’t have any other desktop computers small enough to easily wear my sunglasses.</p>\n\n\n\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t<h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Apple Mac mini (M4)</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Apple-Mac-mini-front-facing-ports.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Apple Mac mini (M4)\" srcset=\"